        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> A mine you deployed is within 100 feet. With a moment's thought, you trigger the detonation of a mine you deployed within 100 feet, causing it to explode in a @Template[type:burst|distance:10]. This mine deals @Damage[(1+ceil(@actor.level/2))d6[fire]] damage, based on the damage type you selected when that mine was deployed. Creatures in the area can attempt a @Check[reflex|dc:resolve(@actor.system.resources.dc.value)|basic] save against your class DC.</p><hr /><p>You can Detonate Mine as a reaction, with the following trigger.</p><p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature enters or leaves a square within the burst area of a mine you have deployed.</p><hr /><p>At 3rd level and every 2 levels thereafter, the damage increases by [[/r 1d6]].</p>",
